thread.title_full: Medisave US LLP reviewed by Jen

author: Jen
title: Jen
text: I bought a stethoscope, it was beautifully engraved. Price was much cheaper than other places I looked into. Was shipped quickly and I appreciated that they required a signature on delivery as this was an expensive purchase. It was nice that they went above and beyond to ensure what I ordered made it to me without any additional cost
